= Configuration Management =

== Features ==

File Support:

 * Binary Files
 * Text files
 * Directories
 * Symlinks

File Attribute support:
 * User/Group ownership
 * Mode Permission
 * selinux permissions


== Getting started ==

== Client utility functions ==

rhncfg-client:
	diff
	get
	list
	elist
	channels
	verify



rhncfg-manager:
	add
	create-channel
	diff
	diff-revisions
	download-channel
	get
	list
	list-channels
	remove
	remove-channel
	revisions
	update
	upload-channel
